Android devices or an ipad can be used as a secondary display for Linux hosts.

Open-Source App Suggestions include:
https://deskreen.com/lang-en
https://github.com/H-M-H/Weylus

For windows: 
The above is appplicable with few closed source apps that are paid/free: 
Duet Display 
https://www.splashtop.com/wiredxdisplay (No Longer updated) 

Sources: 
https://holisticsecurity.io/2019/10/28/android-tablet-or-ipad-as-extra-monitor-for-linux/
